### 询问

![图片描述](data:image/png;base64,) 

### 代码

```
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
</head>

<body>
  <div style="display: flex;">
    <textarea id="htmlTextarea" placeholder="Enter HTML here"></textarea>
    <textarea id="cssTextarea" placeholder="Enter CSS here"></textarea>
  </div>
  <div id="resultDiv"></div>
  <script>
    const htmlTextarea = document.getElementById('htmlTextarea');
    const cssTextarea = document.getElementById('cssTextarea');
    const resultDiv = document.getElementById('resultDiv');

    cssTextarea.addEventListener('input', function () {
      const htmlContent = htmlTextarea.value;
      const styleContent = `<style>${cssTextarea.value}</style>`;
      resultDiv.innerHTML = `${styleContent}${htmlContent}`;
    });
    htmlTextarea.addEventListener('input', function () {
      const htmlContent = htmlTextarea.value;
      const styleContent = `<style>${cssTextarea.value}</style>`;
      resultDiv.innerHTML = `${styleContent}${htmlContent}`;
    });
  </script>
</body>

</html>
```

- html的文本域好用
- css文本域不好用

### 代码

```
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
</head>

<body>
  <div style="display: flex;">
    <textarea id="htmlTextarea" placeholder="Enter HTML here" oninput="updateResult()"></textarea>
    <textarea id="cssTextarea" placeholder="Enter CSS here" oninput="updateResult()"></textarea>
  </div>
  <div id="resultDiv"></div>
  <script>
    function updateResult() {
      const htmlContent = document.getElementById('htmlTextarea').value;
      const cssContent = document.getElementById('cssTextarea').value;
      const styleContent = `<style>${cssContent}</style>`;
      document.getElementById('resultDiv').innerHTML = `${styleContent}${htmlContent}`;
    }
  </script>
</body>

</html>
```

- 左边放到容器中

### 最终代码

```
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    textarea {
      width: 100%;
      height: 500px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      padding: 5px;
      font-size: 14px;

    }

    #resultDiv {
      float:left;
      overflow: auto;
      width:55%;
      height:100%;
      border:1px solid black;
      padding:5px;
      margin:10px;
    }
    div#left {
        float:left;
        width:40%;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div id="left">
    <textarea id="htmlTextarea" placeholder="Enter HTML here" oninput="updateResult()"></textarea>
    <textarea id="cssTextarea" placeholder="Enter CSS here" oninput="updateResult()"></textarea>
  </div>
  <div id="resultDiv"></div>
  <script>
    function updateResult() {
      const htmlContent = document.getElementById('htmlTextarea').value;
      const cssContent = document.getElementById('cssTextarea').value;
      try {
        const styleContent = `<style>${cssContent}</style>`;
        document.getElementById('resultDiv').innerHTML = `${styleContent}${htmlContent}`;
      } catch (error) {
        document.getElementById('resultDiv').innerHTML = `<p>Error: ${error.message}</p>`;
      }
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
```

### 语法高亮

![图片描述](data:image/png;base64,) 

```
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    #left {
      float: left;
      width: 40%;
    }

    #resultDiv {
      float: left;
      overflow: auto;
      width: 55%;
      height: 100%;
      border: 1px solid black;
      padding: 5px;
      margin: 10px;
    }

    .CodeMirror {
      height: 500px;
    }
  </style>
  <!-- 引入 CodeMirror -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/codemirror/5.65.2/codemirror.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/codemirror/5.65.2/theme/monokai.min.css">
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/codemirror/5.65.2/codemirror.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/codemirror/5.65.2/mode/htmlmixed/htmlmixed.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/codemirror/5.65.2/mode/xml/xml.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/codemirror/5.65.2/mode/javascript/javascript.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/codemirror/5.65.2/mode/css/css.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
  <div id="left">
    <label for="htmlTextarea">HTML:</label>
    <textarea id="htmlTextarea" placeholder="Enter HTML here"></textarea>
    <label for="cssTextarea">CSS:</label>
    <textarea id="cssTextarea" placeholder="Enter CSS here"></textarea>
  </div>
  <div id="resultDiv"></div>
  <script>
    // 初始化 CodeMirror 编辑器
    const htmlEditor = CodeMirror.fromTextArea(document.getElementById('htmlTextarea'), {
      mode: "text/html",
      lineNumbers: true,
      theme: "monokai"
    });

    const cssEditor = CodeMirror.fromTextArea(document.getElementById('cssTextarea'), {
      mode: "text/css",
      lineNumbers: true,
      theme: "monokai"
    });

    function updateResult() {
      const htmlContent = htmlEditor.getValue();
      const cssContent = cssEditor.getValue();
      try {
        const styleContent = `<style>${cssContent}</style>`;
        document.getElementById('resultDiv').innerHTML = `${styleContent}${htmlContent}`;
      } catch (error) {
        document.getElementById('resultDiv').innerHTML = `<p>Error: ${error.message}</p>`;
      }
    }

    // 监听编辑器内容变化
    htmlEditor.on("change", updateResult);
    cssEditor.on("change", updateResult);

    // 初始更新结果
    updateResult();
  </script>
</body>

</html>

```

### 字体稍大一些

![图片描述](data:image/png;base64,) 


```
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    body, html {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      height: 100%;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    #container {
      height: 95vh; /* 占据 95% 的视口高度 */
      position: relative;
    }

    #left {
      float: left;
      width: 50%; /* 左侧部分占据 50% 的宽度 */
      height: 100%; /* 占据 100% 的容器高度 */
      border-right: 1px solid black;
    }

    #right {
      float: right;
      width: 50%; /* 右侧部分占据 50% 的宽度 */
      height: 100%; /* 占据 100% 的容器高度 */
      padding: 10px;
      overflow: auto;
    }

    .editor-container {
      height: 50%; /* 每个编辑器容器占据 50% 的高度 */
      margin: 5px;
    }

    .CodeMirror {
      height: 100%; /* 编辑器高度占满容器 */
      font-size: 20px; /* 设置字体大小 */
    }

    #resultDiv {
      border: 1px solid black;
      padding: 5px;
      margin: 5px;
      overflow: auto;
      height: 100%; /* 占据 100% 的容器高度 */
    }

    /* 清除浮动 */
    .clearfix::after {
      content: "";
      display: table;
      clear: both;
    }
  </style>
  <!-- 引入 CodeMirror -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/codemirror/5.65.2/codemirror.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/codemirror/5.65.2/theme/monokai.min.css">
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/codemirror/5.65.2/codemirror.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/codemirror/5.65.2/mode/htmlmixed/htmlmixed.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/codemirror/5.65.2/mode/xml/xml.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/codemirror/5.65.2/mode/javascript/javascript.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/codemirror/5.65.2/mode/css/css.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
  <div id="container" class="clearfix">
    <div id="left">
      <div class="editor-container">
        <label for="htmlTextarea">HTML:</label>
        <textarea id="htmlTextarea" placeholder="Enter HTML here"></textarea>
      </div>
      <div class="editor-container">
        <label for="cssTextarea">CSS:</label>
        <textarea id="cssTextarea" placeholder="Enter CSS here"></textarea>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="right">
      <div id="resultDiv"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <script>
    // 初始化 CodeMirror 编辑器
    const htmlEditor = CodeMirror.fromTextArea(document.getElementById('htmlTextarea'), {
      mode: "text/html",
      lineNumbers: true,
      theme: "monokai"
    });

    const cssEditor = CodeMirror.fromTextArea(document.getElementById('cssTextarea'), {
      mode: "text/css",
      lineNumbers: true,
      theme: "monokai"
    });

    function updateResult() {
      const htmlContent = htmlEditor.getValue();
      const cssContent = cssEditor.getValue();
      try {
        const styleContent = `<style>${cssContent}</style>`;
        document.getElementById('resultDiv').innerHTML = `${styleContent}${htmlContent}`;
      } catch (error) {
        document.getElementById('resultDiv').innerHTML = `<p>Error: ${error.message}</p>`;
      }
    }

    // 监听编辑器内容变化
    htmlEditor.on("change", updateResult);
    cssEditor.on("change", updateResult);

    // 初始更新结果
    updateResult();

    // 使编辑器高度可调整
    window.addEventListener('resize', () => {
      htmlEditor.setSize(null, null); // 自动调整高度
      cssEditor.setSize(null, null); // 自动调整高度
    });
  </script>
</body>

</html>
```
